    $(p "Your cognitive energy is precious. JEM AI must reduce friction. This is the 'why' behind the simple aliases and the 'super f***ing easy' UI philosophy.")

    $(h1 "CHAPTER 2: JEM AI'S UNIFIED CORE ARCHITECTURE")
    $(p "We evolved from a complex 'Two Brains' system to a single, powerful, integrated 'House' architecture.")
    $(h2 "Introducing 'jemai_core.py' - The True Brain of JEM AI")
